      "text": "The [[NixOS]] solution is to have one unified configuration file that specifies everything: kernel version, kernel parameters, package versions, package patches, etc. You can change any detail and then make an incremental rebootstrap that updates only the affected components. You can share by pushing the system configuration source code to a Git repository and then anybody can use that to bootstrap the same environment. -- [https://groups.google.com/g/snabb-devel/c/8BTftZL0oMo/m/V2E2SwgBCAAJ groups]\n"
